---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About — Global Wealth Portfolio"
  description="Global Wealth Portfolio is a private, browser-based wealth dashboard for tracking investments, expenses, loans, and goals across 30+ currencies."
>
  <section class="container-page page-section pt-3xl pb-2xl max-w-3xl">
    <p class="text-caption-mono text-body mb-xs">About</p>
    <h1 class="text-display-lg mb-lg">Our mission: make financial tracking private, simple, and borderless.</h1>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      Global Wealth Portfolio was built because we believe your financial data
      belongs to you &mdash; not to a bank, a fintech startup, or an advertising
      platform. Every design decision we make starts from that conviction.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">Why we built this</h2>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      The existing tools for tracking personal finances fall into two camps:
      desktop software that is powerful but clunky, or cloud apps that are
      convenient but mine your data. Neither respects the fact that money is
      deeply personal. We wanted a third option &mdash; an app that is as
      polished as the best SaaS products but runs entirely on your own device.
    </p>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      We are a small, independent team passionate about privacy, good design,
      and building tools that genuinely improve people's financial lives. We
      do not take venture capital, we do not sell data, and we do not plan
      to. The app is and will remain free, open-source, and local-first.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">What makes us different</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-lg space-y-xs text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      <li><strong>100% local-first.</strong> Your data never leaves your device. No servers, no cloud sync, no third-party access.</li>
      <li><strong>Privacy by design.</strong> No account creation, no email verification, no tracking scripts, no cookies.</li>
      <li><strong>Multi-currency by default.</strong> Born global &mdash; 30+ currencies, 10+ languages, RTL support.</li>
      <li><strong>AI that works for you.</strong> On-device OCR for bank statements, smart categorization, and projections &mdash; all running in your browser.</li>
      <li><strong>Open source (MIT).</strong> You can inspect every line of code, fork the project, or run your own instance.</li>
      <li><strong>Free forever.</strong> No tiers, no paywalls, no upsells. Every feature is available from the first click.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">Our values</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-md mb-md">
      <div class="card-soft p-lg">
        <h3 class="text-display-sm mb-sm">Privacy first</h3>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-body">We believe financial data is the most personal data you have. It should never be collected, analysed, or monetised by anyone but you.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-soft p-lg">
        <h3 class="text-display-sm mb-sm">Borderless by design</h3>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-body">Your financial life spans currencies and countries. Your tracking tool should too &mdash; without charging you for currency conversion or region locking features.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-soft p-lg">
        <h3 class="text-display-sm mb-sm">Radical simplicity</h3>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-body">Finance is complex enough. The tools you use should reduce complexity, not add to it. Every feature we build must justify its existence.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-soft p-lg">
        <h3 class="text-display-sm mb-sm">Built in the open</h3>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-body">Open source means accountable. Anyone can audit our code, verify our privacy claims, and contribute. No black boxes, no opaque algorithms.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">The team</h2>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      Global Wealth Portfolio is maintained by a small team of engineers and
      designers who believe that great financial software does not need to
      compromise on privacy. We are distributed across time zones and
      currencies ourselves, so we eat our own dogfood every day.
    </p>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body">
      Want to contribute? The project is open source on
      <a href="https://github.com/sourabh6303/globalwealthfolio" class="text-link hover:underline" rel="noopener" target="_blank">GitHub</a>.
      Issues, pull requests, and feature suggestions are always welcome.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
